I"€<p>Welcome to Ordinary Differential Equations I.</p>

<p>The prerequisites are as follows:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Single variable differential and integral calculus.</li>
  <li>A first course in linear algbera</li>
  <li>An exposure to physics is useful; many examples will be drawn from physics.</li>
  <li>A concurrent course in multivariable calculus will be useful</li>
</ol>

